<main>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section id="home" class="hero">
    <div class="hero-watermark"></div>
    <div class="hero-card-wrapper">
      <div class="hero-card hero-content">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <h1>Connecting Sub-Saharan Africa with reliable European process and packaging solutions.</h1>
          <div class="cta-row">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contact">Request a consult</a>
            <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#services">Our services</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-stats">
          <div class="stat-title">Africa</div>
          <hr>
          <div class="stat-row">
            <div>
              <div class="stat-number">100+</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Projects</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="stat-number">4+</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Partners</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section id="about">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h3>About Us</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid-wrapper">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>For years, we watched world-class European processing and packaging technology struggle to gain ground in Africa. The challenge was never the equipment. It was the missing local partner. PPSA was founded to close that gap with regional insight, hands-on support and a focus on long-term results.</p>
        <p>We are a family-owned company representing leading manufacturers such as Pattyn, Gerstenberg Services, API Schmidt-Bretten and Daniatech. Our work spans Sub-Saharan Africa, where clients rely on us for solutions that fit their exact needs.</p>
        <p>What sets us apart is our approach. We get to know each operation, build lasting relationships and stay involved long after installation. Clients trust us for practical guidance, quick support and a team that shows up when it matters.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section id="services">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h3>Services</h3>
      <p class="muted">End-to-end support across the project lifecycle.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><h4>Representation</h4><p class="muted">Evaluation, feasibility, pricing and partner selection.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>Training</h4><p class="muted">Operator and maintenance training supported by documentation and knowledge transfer.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>Support & spares</h4><p class="muted">Local warranty handling, spare parts and after-sales support.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Partners -->
  <section id="partners">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h3>Our Partners</h3>
      <p class="muted">Leading manufacturers we represent in Africa.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="partners">
      <a href="https://www.pattyn.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partner"><img src="assets/img/partners/Pattyn_Logo.png" alt="Pattyn"></a>
      <a href="https://www.apischmidt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partner"><img src="assets/img/partners/API_Logo.png" alt="API Schmidt-Bretten"></a>
      <a href="https://www.gerstenberg.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partner"><img src="assets/img/partners/Gerstenberg_Logo.png" alt="Gerstenberg Services"></a>
      <a href="https://www.daniatech.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partner"><img src="assets/img/partners/Daniatech_Logo.png" alt="Daniatech"></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Markets -->
  <section id="markets">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h3>Regions</h3>
      <!--
      <p class="muted">Primary regions we support</p>
      -->
    </div>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><h4>Southern Africa (SADC)</h4><p class="muted">Serving South Africa, Angola, Mozambique, Namibia, Botswana, Zimbabwe, Zambia, Malawi, Eswatini, Lesotho, Tanzania, DRC with local expertise and hands-on support.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>West Africa (ECOWAS)</h4><p class="muted">Connecting businesses in Nigeria, Ghana, Benin, Burkina Faso, Gabon, Ivory Coast, Gambia, Guinea, Liberia, Mali, Niger, Senegal, Sierra Leone, Togo to reliable European processing and packaging solutions.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>East Africa (EAC & more)</h4><p class="muted">Supporting Kenya, Ethiopia, Uganda, Tanzania, Rwanda, Burundi, South Sudan, Madagascar, Mauritius, Seychelles, Somalia, with tailored solutions and ongoing technical guidance.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Industries -->
  <section id="industries">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h3>Industries</h3>
      <!--
      <p class="muted">Industries we support.</p>
      -->
    </div>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><h4>Mixing & heat treatment for hygienic processing</h4><p class="muted">Advanced mixing, powder handling and heat treatment technology for dairy, beverages, food and home and personal care applications.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>Processing technology for yellow fat and edible oil</h4><p class="muted">Innovative Gerstenberg processing, crystallization and texturizing technology for margarine, shortening, ghee, spreads, CBS, butter and related products.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>Bag-in-box packaging solutions</h4><p class="muted">Pattyn automated systems integrating bag forming, filling, sealing and case packing for industries such as frozen foods, nuts, bakery, confectionery and industrial goods.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>Plate heat exchangers</h4><p class="muted">Schmidt® plate heat exchangers for hygienic and industrial processing, including gasketed, semi-welded, double-wall and brazed configurations.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section id="contact">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h3>Contact</h3>
      <p class="muted">Tell us about your requirement and we’ll set up a call.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-grid-wrapper">
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <form method="POST" action="https://formspree.io/f/your-form-id">
          <label for="name">Your name</label>
          <input id="name" name="name" type="text" placeholder="Jane Doe" required>

          <label for="company">Company</label>
          <input id="company" name="company" type="text" placeholder="Company name">

          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@company.com" required>

          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Tell us briefly about your requirement" required></textarea>

          <div class="form-cta">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Send enquiry</button>
            <div class="small">
              Or email: <a href="mailto:info@pps-africa.com">info@pps-africa.com</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>

        <aside class="card">
          <h4>Office</h4>
          <p class="small">Cape Town, South Africa</p>
          <hr>
          <h4>Emergency</h4>
          <p class="small">Phone: +27 83 676 2317</p>
          <p class="small">Email: <a href="mailto:geert.verbeemen@pps-africa.com">geert.verbeemen@pps-africa.com</a></p>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

